Kame
====

Kame is a plugin which permits to manage ajax table. The table structure is defined in controller. 
It generates an action +[....]_kame+ in controller and an helper for views.

It refers to the japanese turtle äº€. 

Example
=======

  TurtleController < ApplicationController
    kame :turtles do |t|
      t.column :name
      t.column :weight
      t.column :name, :though=>:country
      t.action :update
      t.action :delete 
    end

    def index
    end

    # Manage action create, update...

  end


